text: Raminho is a parish in the municipality of Angra do Heroísmo on the island of Terceira in the Azores. The population in 2011 was 565,Instituto Nacional de Estatística in an area of 11.07 km².Eurostat It consists of the localities Cabo do Raminho and Raminho. ==References== ==External links== * http://www.acores.com/raminho Category:Parishes of Angra do Heroísmo
